            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Version 3.3</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>New: Convert right from Finder</strong> — right-click any WAV or AIFF file (or folder) and choose "Convert to M4A - JessOS" or "Convert to M4A (Folder) - JessOS". Enabled automatically the first time you launch the app.</li>
    <li>The old entry in Finder's Services submenu has been replaced by the new right-click menu items</li>
    <li>Smaller app with simplified internals</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
